text: Stefanie Tücking (1 April 1962 – 1 December 2018) was a German radio and television presenter. She was born in Kaiserslautern, Germany. In Germany, Tücking worked for the German broadcaster Südwestrundfunk (SWR) as a television and radio presenter. Tücking was found dead in Baden-Baden, Germany on 1 December 2018 at the age of 56. ==References== ==Other websites== * www.tuecking.com — official site * Category:1962 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Deaths from cardiac arrest Category:German television presenters Category:Radio personalities
